Package: gteatime
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: lightweight GTK3 system-tray tea and coffee timer
 GTK3 tray timer for tea and coffee presets written in C inspired by
 kteatime.  It uses StatusNotifierItem over D-Bus when available and
 falls back to the XEmbed system tray protocol on X11.
